Go read SCP-4297 first, if you haven't already!

This is my fourth article, based on the mainlist SCP of the same number. Kind of.

Incidentally, I published this within 24 hours of publishing the main one. Two skips in one day! (According to some more experienced authors, this is the first time anyone's published a mainlist scip and its -J in such a short time cool!) (Sorry for the brag.)

Thanks to Crashington and TheBlueHour for looking through my draft on such short notice. No rush on the next one, eh?

